quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  14,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  14,1,Alif Laaam Raa ( yeh ) aik ( purnoor ) kitaab ( hai ) is ko hum ne tum par is liye nazilkiya hai ke logon ko andheray se nikaal kar roshni ki taraf le jao ( yani ) un ke perwar-digaar ke hukum se ghalib aur qabil tareef ( khuda ) ke raste ki taraf
  14,2,woh khuda ke jo kuch asmano aur zameen mein hai sab isi ka hai. aur kafiroon ke liye azaab sakht ( ki wajah ) se kharabi hai
  14,3,jo akhirat ki nisbat duniya ko pasand karte aur ( logon ko ) khuda ke raste se roktay aur is mein kajji chahtay hain. yeh log parlay suray ki gumraahi mein hain
  14,4,aur hum ne koi paighambar nahi bheja magar apni qoum ki zabaan boltaa tha taakay inhen ( ehkaam khuda ) khol khol kar bta day. phir khuda jisay chahta hai gumraah karta hai aur jisay chahta hai hadaayat deta hai aur woh ghalib ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  14,5,aur hum ne moose ko apni nishanain day kar bheja ke apni qoum ko tareqi se nikaal kar roshni mein le jao. aur un ko khuda ke din yaad dilao is mein un logon ke liye jo sabir o shakir hain ( qudrat khuda ki ) nishanain hain
  14,6,aur jab moose ne apni qoum se kaha ke khuda ne jo tum par mehrbanian ki hain un ko yaad karo jab ke tum ko firaon ki qoum ( ke haath ) se mukhlasi di woh log tumhe buray azaab dete they aur tumahray beiton ko maar daaltay they aur aurat zaat yani tumhari larkiyon ko zindah rehne dete they aur is mein tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se barri ( sakht ) azmaish thi
  14,7,aur jab tumahray perwar-digaar ne ( tum ko ) aagah kiya ke agar shukar karo ge to mein tumhe ziyada dun ga aur agar nashukri karo ge to ( yaad rakho ke ) mera azaab bhi sakht hai
  14,8,aur moose ne ( saaf saaf ) keh diya ke agar tum aur jitne aur log zameen mein hain sab ke sab nashukri karo to khuda bhi be niaz ( aur ) qabil tareef hai
  14,9,bhala tum ko un logon ( ke halaat ) ki khabar nahi pohanchi jo tum se pehlay they ( yani ) Nooh aur Aad aur smod ki qoum. aur jo un ke baad they. jin ka ilm khuda ke siwa kisi ko nahi ( jab ) un ke paas paighambar nishanain le kar aeye to unhon ne apne haath un ke monhon par rakh diye ( ke khamosh raho ) aur kehnay lagey ke hum to tumhari risalat ko tasleem nahi karte aur jis cheez ki taraf tum hamein bulatay ho hum is se quwwat shak mein hain
  14,10,un ke payghambaroon ne kahakiya ( tum ko ) khuda ( ke baray ) mein shak hai jo asmano aur zameen ka peda karne wala hai. woh tumhe is liye bulaataa hai ke tumahray gunah bakhshay aur ( faida pohanchanay ke liye ) aik muddat muqarrar taq tum ko mohlat day. woh bolay ke tum to hamaray hi jaisay aadmi ho. tumhara yeh Mansha hai ke jin cheezon ko hamaray barray pujte rahay hain un ( ke poojnay ) se hum ko band kar do to ( acha ) koi khuli Daleel lao ( yani moujza dikhao )
  14,11,payghambaroon ne un se kaha ke haan hum tumahray hi jaisay aadmi hain. lekin khuda apne bundon mein se jis ko chahta hai ( nabuwat ka ) ahsaan karta hai aur hamaray ikhtiyar ki baat nahi ke hum khuda ke hukum ke baghair tum ko ( tumhari farmaaish ke mutabiq ) moujza deikhein aur khuda hi par mominoun ko bharosa rakhna chahiye
  14,12,aur hum kyonkr khuda par bharosa nah rakhen halaank is ne hum ko hamaray ( deen ke seedhay ) raste betaye hain. jo takleifein tum hum ko dete ho is par sabr karen ge. aur ahal tawakkal ko khuda hi par bharosa rakhna chahiye
  14,13,aur jo kafir they unhon ne apne payghambaroon se kaha ke ( ya to ) hum tum ko apne malik se bahar nikaal den ge ya hamaray mazhab mein daakhil ho jao. to perwar-digaar ne un ki taraf wahi bhaije ke hum zaalmon ko halaak kar den ge
  14,14,aur un ke baad tum ko is zameen mein abad karen ge. yeh is shakhs ke liye hai jo ( qayamat ke roz ) mere samnay kharray honay se daray aur mere azaab se khauf kere
  14,15,aur payghambaroon ne ( khuda se apni ) fatah chahi to har sarkash ziddi namuraad reh gaya
  14,16,is ke peechay dozakh hai aur usay peep ka pani pilaya jaye ga
  14,17,woh is ko ghoont ghoont piye ga aur gilaay se nahi utaar sakay ga aur har taraf se usay mout aa rahi hogi magar woh marnay mein nahi aeye ga. aur is ke peechay sakht azaab hoga
  14,18,jin logon ne apne perwar-digaar se kufarkiya un ke aamaal ki misaal raakh ki si hai ke aandhi ke din is par zor ki howa chalay ( aur ) usay ura le jaye ( is terhan ) jo kaam woh karte rahay un par un ko kuch dustarus nah hogi. yahi to parlay suray ki gumraahi hai
  14,19,kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke khuda ne asmano aur zameen ko tadbeer se pedakiya hai. agar woh chahay to tum ko nabood kar day aur ( tumhari jagah ) nai makhlooq peda kar day
  14,20,aur yeh khuda ko kuch bhi mushkil nahi
  14,21,"aur ( qayamat ke din ) sab log khuda ke samnay kharray hon ge to zaeef ( al-aqal muttabe apne (roaa,saa )mutakabareen se kahin ge ke hum to tumahray pairo they.kiya tum khuda ka kuch azaab hum par se dafaa kar saktay ho. woh kahin ge ke agar khuda hum ko hadaayat karta to hum tum ko hadaayat karte. ab hum ghbrayin ya zid karen hamaray haq mein barabar hai. koi jagah ( guraiz aur ) rihayi ki hamaray liye nahi hai"
  14,22,jab ( hisaab kitaab ka ) kaam faisla ho chukay ga to shetan kahe ga ( jo ) wada khuda ne tum sekiya tha ( woh to ) sacha ( tha ) aur ( jo ) wada mein ne tum sekiya tha woh jhoota tha. aur mera tum par kisi terhan ka zor nahi tha. haan mein ne tum ko ( gumraahi aur baatil ki taraf ) bulaya to tum ne ( jaldi se aur be Daleel ) mera kaha maan liya. to ( aaj ) mujhe malamat nah karo. apne aap hi ko malamat karo. nah mein tumhari faryaad rassi karsaktha hon aur nah tum meri faryaad rassi kar saktay ho. mein is baat se inkaar karta hon ke tum pehlay mujhe shareek banatay they. be shak jo zalim hain un ke liye dard dainay wala azaab hai
  14,23,aur jo imaan laaye aur amal naik kiye woh bahishtoon mein daakhil kiye jayen ge jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain apne perwar-digaar ke hukum se hamesha un mein rahen ge. wahan un ki sahib salamat salam hoga
  14,24,kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke khuda ne pak baat ki kaisi misaal bayan farmai hai ( woh aisi hai ) jaisay pakeeza darakht jis ki jarr mazboot ( yani zameen ko pakdae hue ) ho aur shaakhen aasman mein
  14,25,apne perwar-digaar ke hukum se har waqt phal lata ( aur meway deta ) ho. aur khuda logon ke liye misalein bayan farmata hai taakay woh nasiyaat pakren
  14,26,aur napak baat ki misaal napak darakht ki si hai ( nah jarr mustahkam nah shaakhen buland ) zameen ke oopar hi se akheer kar pheink diya jaye ga is ko zara bhi qarar ( o sabaat ) nahi
  14,27,khuda mominoun ( ke dilon ) ko ( sahih aur ) paki baat se duniya ki zindagi mein bhi mazboot rakhta hai aur akhirat mein bhi ( rakhay ga ) aur khuda be insafon ko gumraah kar deta hai aur khuda jo chahta hai karta hai
  14,28,kiya tum ne un logon ko nahi dekha jinhon ne khuda ke ahsaan ko nashukri se badal diya. aur apni qoum ko tabahi ke ghar mein utaara
  14,29,( woh ghar ) dozakh hai. ( sab nashukray ) is mein daakhil hon ge. aur woh bura thikana hai
  14,30,aur un logon ne khuda ke shareek muqarrar kiye ke ( logon ko ) is ke raste se gumraah karen. keh do ke ( chand roz ) faiday utha lau aakhir kaar tum ko dozakh ki taraf lout kar jana hai
  14,31,( ae paighambar ) mere momin bundon se keh do ke namaz parha karen aur is din ke anay se peshtar jis mein nah ( aamaal ka ) soda hoga aur nah dosti ( kaam aeye gi ) hamaray diye hue maal mein se darparda aur zahir kharch karte rahen
  14,32,khuda hi to hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko pedakiya aur aasman se meen barsaya phir is se tumahray khanay ke liye phal peda kiye. aur kashtiyon ( aur jahazoo ) ko tumahray zair farmaankiya taakay darya ( aur samandar ) mein is ke hukum se chalein. aur nﮦron ko bhi tumahray zair farmaankiya
  14,33,aur Sooraj aur chaand ko tumahray liye kaam mein laga diya ke dono ( din raat ) aik dastoor par chal rahay hain. aur raat aur din ko bhi tumhari khatir kaam mein laga diya
  14,34,aur jo kuch tum ne manga sab mein se tum ko inayatkiya. aur agar khuda ke ahsaan ginnay lagu to shumaar nah krsko. ( magar log nematon ka shukar nahi karte ) kuch shak nahi ke ensaan bara be insaaf aur nashukara hai
  14,35,aur jab ibrahim ne dua ki ke mere perwar-digaar is shehar ko ( logon ke liye ) aman ki jagah bana day. aur mujhe aur meri aulaad ko is baat se ke buton ki parastish karne lagen bachaaye rakh
  14,36,ae perwar-digaar unhon ne bohat se logon ko gumraahkiya hai. so jis shakhs ne mera kaha maana woh mera hai. aur jis ne meri nafarmani ki to too bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  14,37,ae perwar-digaar mein ne apni aulaad ko maidan ( mecca ) mein jahan khaiti nahi tairay izzat ( o adab v ) walay ghar ke paas laa basai hai. ae perwar-digaar taakay yeh namaz parheen to logon ke dilon ko aisa kar day ke un ki taraf jhuke rahen aur un ko meoon se rozi day taakay ( tera ) shukar karen
  14,38,ae perwar-digaar jo baat hum chupatay aur jo zahir karte hain to sab jaanta hai. aur khuda se koi cheez makhfi nahi ( nah ) zameen mein nah aasman mein
  14,39,khuda ka shukar hai jis ne mujh ko barri Umar mein ismael aur Ishaq bakhshay. be shak mera perwar-digaar suneney wala hai
  14,40,ae perwar-digaar mujh ko ( aisi tofeq inayat ) kar ke namaz parhta rahon aur meri aulaad ko bhi ( yeh tofeq bakhash ) ae perwar-digaar meri dua qubool farma
  14,41,ae perwar-digaar hisaab ( kitaab ) ke din mujh ko aur mere maa baap ko aur mominoun ko mughfirat kejio
  14,42,aur ( momino ) mat khayaal karna ke yeh zalim jo amal kar rahay hain khuda un se be khabar hai. woh un ko is din taq mohlat day raha hai jab ke ( dehshat ke sabab ) ankhen khuli ki khuli reh jayen gi
  14,43,( aur log ) sir uthaye hue ( maidan qayamat ki taraf ) daud rahay hon ge un ki nigehain un ki taraf lout nah saken gi aur un ke dil ( maaray khauf ke ) howa ho rahay hon ge
  14,44,aur logon ko is din se aagah kardo jab un par azaab aajay ga tab zalim log kahin ge ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar hamein thori si muddat mohlat ataa kar. taakay teri dawat ( toheed ) qubool karen aur ( tairay ) payghambaroon ke peechay chalein ( to jawab miley ga )kiya tum pehlay kasmain nahi khaya karte they ke tum ko ( is haal se jis mein tum ho ) zawaal ( aur qayamat ko hisaab aamaal ) nahi hoga
  14,45,aur jo log apne aap par zulm karte they tum un ke makanon mein rehtay they aur tum par zahir hochuka tha ke hum ne un logon ke sath kis terhan ( ka maamla )kiya tha aur tumahray ( samjhane ) ke liye misalein bayan kar di theen
  14,46,aur unhon ne ( barri barri ) tadbeerye kee aur un ki ( sab ) tadbeerye khuda ke haan ( likhi hui ) hain go woh tadbeerye aisi ( ghazab ki ) theen ke un se pahar bhi tal jayen
  14,47,to aisa khayaal nah karna ke khuda ne jo apne payghambaroon se wadakiya hai is ke khilaaf kere ga be shak khuda zabardast ( aur ) badla lainay wala hai
  14,48,jis din yeh zameen doosri zameen se badal di jaye gi aur aasman bhi ( badal diye jayen ge ) aur sab log khuday-e Yagana o zabardast ke samnay nikal kharray hon ge
  14,49,aur is din tum gunahgaaron ko dekho ge ke zanjeeroon mein jakray hue hain
  14,50,un ke karte gandhak ke hon ge aur un ke monhon ko aag lapait rahi hogi
  14,51,yeh is liye ke khuda har shakhs ko is ke aamaal ka badla day. be shak khuda jald hisaab lainay wala hai
  14,52,yeh quran logon ke naam ( khuda ka pegham ) hai taakay un ko is se daraya jaye aur taakay woh jaan len ke wohi akela mabood hai aur taakay ahal aqal nasiyaat pakren
